            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"特朗普斥責北約為「懦夫」 不滿盟友未能協助重開霍爾木茲海峽\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2oHe4u2nO1PkUdy_9J581A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/c89f7d80-2482-11f1-b77c-c8f29195dbff\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">特朗普斥責北約為「懦夫」 不滿盟友未能協助重開霍爾木茲海峽</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
